Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.60,0:00:02.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Class 3-B?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.77,0:00:04.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Kuroi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:05.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.71,0:01:32.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for treating us today, Cousin Yui!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.57,0:01:33.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Anytime!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.15,0:01:35.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:37.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That was good, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.93,0:01:38.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.64,0:01:41.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you feel happy when the egg tastes good?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.64,0:01:45.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The price of gas went up two yen since yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.70,0:01:49.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Should've filled up the tank...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.54,0:01:49.17,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}Why is it that people who spend generously...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:52.00,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}...care so much about a one yen difference in the price of gasoline?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.34,0:01:54.38,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(444,228)}There\N Over\N Here
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.65,0:01:55.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.32,0:01:58.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That book I lent you a while ago is\N apparently getting turned into a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.20,0:01:59.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be buying it though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.97,0:02:01.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so behind, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.12,0:02:05.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I reserved the limited edition as soon as it was announced.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.70,0:02:08.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I even bought the DVD box set for\N the anime and other related goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.42,0:02:10.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're more hooked than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.92,0:02:14.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty common for people to become bigger\N fans than the people who recommend stuff to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.00,0:02:16.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how Cousin Yui chose her car.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.65,0:02:17.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to someone else's influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.86,0:02:18.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Her car?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.36,0:02:21.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I lent her a racing manga...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.55,0:02:23.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That sure surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.30,0:02:25.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's scary how much energy people put into their hobbies...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:27.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday was the third win in a row, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.77,0:02:30.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the start of a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:32.04,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}If they keep on winning...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:33.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:35.17,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}...the playoffs and Japan Series aren't out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.46,0:02:35.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably pro baseball, I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.17,0:02:37.30,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}All the way to the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.75,0:02:37.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher enjoys it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.32,0:02:38.84,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Besides, baseball's all about...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.03,0:02:38.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of baseball...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:41.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The famous poet, Shiki Masaoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.57,0:02:43.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...apparently loved baseball a great deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.70,0:02:45.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,He played catcher...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:48.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...until he was too ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.79,0:02:51.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And he took his childhood name, Noboru...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.29,0:02:53.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...wrote it using the characters for baseball...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.08,0:02:54.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and pronounced it Noball.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.88,0:02:55.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.96,0:02:59.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The winners of the Major League\N are called the world champions, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:02.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Talking about the Japan Series reminded me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.74,0:03:03.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:05.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when it only includes American teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.83,0:03:11.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, they should beat our team before\N they call themselves world champions, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:13.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's awfully pumped up...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:16.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure stinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:17.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure does.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.42,0:03:18.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:18.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.80,0:03:19.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:21.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.18,0:03:23.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Teach me how to do these!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:26.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:28.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You asking a question about schoolwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.00,0:03:32.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Some of these problems are quite difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:36.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's cause they're from an arcade quiz game.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.69,0:03:39.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not good with academic stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:41.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go again...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:43.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And put more effort into your studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.53,0:03:44.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're applying for college.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.10,0:03:47.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I may be like this here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.81,0:03:50.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but they call me a sage over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.70,0:03:51.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.64,0:03:54.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...just enroll in that whatever academy of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.83,0:03:57.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why I didn't get enough sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:58.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How long were you up playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:01.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You say you're always in bed by eleven, Miyuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:03.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's early.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:04.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:06.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:06.05,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(159,303)}「Sleeping helps
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:06.05,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(482,304)}you grow ☆」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.37,0:04:09.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So I was thinking when I looked at Miyuki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.12,0:04:12.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you haven't grown much considering how much you sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:14.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what Big Sister said.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:16.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sensitive about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:19.36,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(313,50)}That night, around 9 o'clock
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:22.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me for calling so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.05,0:04:23.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Kobayakawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.72,0:04:25.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the Iwasaki residence?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:26.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.64,0:04:27.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,May I speak with Minami-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:30.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She already went to bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.27,0:04:32.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did she always sleep this early?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.62,0:04:55.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're having fun singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.08,0:04:58.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we'll make do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.13,0:04:59.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.54,0:05:00.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.23,0:05:02.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let my father know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:04.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,After the ground-breaking ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:06.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:08.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.76,0:05:10.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, there you go again...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.33,0:05:12.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm underage, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:13.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:15.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.83,0:05:17.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:17.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.17,0:05:18.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:21.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Kagami...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.63,0:05:23.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't see you gesturing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.96,0:05:25.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.13,0:05:26.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a force of habit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.82,0:05:27.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.41,0:05:32.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm on the phone, I have to concentrate so I stop gaming...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:35.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but then my empty hand starts feeling lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.54,0:05:37.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:38.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.50,0:05:43.42,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I was using a roller to get rid of dust the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:45.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Roll! Roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.05,0:05:47.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff like that can get pretty addictive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:50.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Like random doodling or menial chores.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.05,0:05:52.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.22,0:05:56.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you get off the phone, that stuff gets old really fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:05:59.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kinda depressing when only the area around you is clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:02.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You could just finish the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.48,0:06:04.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,My passion fades with the conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:06.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So you just leave it like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:10.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy's kinda stinky, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.91,0:06:12.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's okay every now and then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:14.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:15.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,**cky!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.02,0:06:15.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Po***!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:17.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:19.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...back in grade school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:20.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:21.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a little kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:23.69,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:25.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of things we did when we were little...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:27.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I used to stir my yogurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:29.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and go, "Bread factory!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:32.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bread factory?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,0:06:34.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't heard of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:38.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.64,0:06:40.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Bread factory?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:41.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be embarrassed. Just 'fess up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.88,0:06:42.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:45.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,About that game I lent you back during first semester...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:47.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone else wants to play it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.19,0:06:48.01,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:48.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:49.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it for the squirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:51.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Reminds me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:53.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've lent a bunch to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:54.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I should get them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.47,0:06:56.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you sure are amazing, Hiiragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:57.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.62,0:06:58.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.08,0:07:01.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The other day, I found these games and\N didn't remember who I borrowed them from...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.79,0:07:03.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed you can remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:04.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:07.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And there are some I lent to other people that I've forgotten about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:09.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're way too careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.15,0:07:09.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.84,0:07:12.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's gotta be a Law of Equal Lending.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:14.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a universal principle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:15.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,As if...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:21.87,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.87,0:07:22.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.38,0:07:24.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiiragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:24.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:25.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Misao.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.67,0:07:26.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, what's u—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.88,0:07:29.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:30.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad, Potemkin...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.59,0:07:31.51,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:32.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:33.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:34.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No big deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.47,0:07:35.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:35.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:36.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:38.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:41.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What was it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:42.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:44.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It was something super important...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:45.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget it if it's important.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:48.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking at the numbers for the Autumn Jumbo Lottery...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:50.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but mine were all off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:51.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess it's not so easy to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.51,0:07:54.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I sent in a bunch of postcards...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:56.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I didn't win any prizes from the drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.49,0:07:57.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:07:58.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.89,0:08:01.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When you never win...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.02,0:08:05.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you start to wonder if the vendors or\N editors are running some kind of scam, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:06.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.65,0:08:08.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be so suspicious of other people!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:11.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No good...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:13.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm gonna call it a night.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:17.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll go to the bathroom first.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.50,0:08:22.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They tell me that I talk to myself too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.71,0:08:24.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But that don't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.71,0:08:30.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was really sleepy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:34.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...so why am I so awake after that weird joke?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:36.49,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(319,40)}Next day, dead of night
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:39.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I really can't do this at night.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.03,0:08:40.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not feeling it tonight...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:42.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I should get to bed while I'm dozing off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.48,0:08:47.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's freezing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:51.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was really sleepy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.44,0:08:55.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...so why am I so awake just 'cause it's cold under the covers?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.91,0:08:58.18,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(321,39)}The day {\fs22}after that{\fs26}, dead of night
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:08:58.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's useless...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.24,0:08:59.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's warm tonight...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.49,0:09:00.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe I can fall asleep quickly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.08,0:09:07.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My legs are really hot for some reason...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:08.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't fall asleep!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.96,0:09:10.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why is that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.71,0:09:13.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Does this only happen to me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.70,0:09:19.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the season for baked sweet potatoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:20.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Kagami...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.53,0:09:21.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:22.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:24.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, so don't say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:25.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:26.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:27.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you'll gain weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.62,0:09:28.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You still said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.73,0:09:30.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't help it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:32.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I've made eye contact with the guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.63,0:09:34.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...it'd be rude not to buy one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:34.84,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:36.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"Will she buy one?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.59,0:09:38.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,"My feelings will be hurt if she doesn't."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.70,0:09:39.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That look!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:41.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.04,0:09:43.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If you make eye contact at Comiket...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.33,0:09:44.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's really hard to put a book back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.29,0:09:48.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't care when other people have\N no idea what you're talking about, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.54,0:09:49.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:52.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about when you're hanging around a circle's booth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.46,0:09:54.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When you pick up a book in front of a sales rep...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:57.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you feel pretty bad if you leave without buying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.74,0:09:59.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you still put it back, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.97,0:10:04.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's been an increase in the number\N of light novels being adapted to anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.06,0:10:04.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.23,0:10:06.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,The novel I lent you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:09.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...has already had three anime adaptations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.06,0:10:10.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And there should be a new volume coming out soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.06,0:10:12.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I've watched the anime...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:14.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I haven't read the novels.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:16.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Too much text makes me tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:17.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That again, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.95,0:10:21.03,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't the games you always play have a lot more text?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.70,0:10:24.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They should, but it's weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:27.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd really help if they released them in a visual novel format.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.66,0:10:28.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:29.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:31.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,When are they doing the fourth season of the anime?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.40,0:10:32.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.31,0:10:33.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:34.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that some kind of reference?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.39,0:10:47.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:49.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:52.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The lid always ends up crooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.94,0:10:55.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, some people are like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.73,0:10:57.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's clumsiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.63,0:10:59.28,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I do it all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:00.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:04.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You share some cute flaws with Miyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:05.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.79,0:11:08.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are amazing, Big Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.79,0:11:14.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do, Big Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.34,0:11:15.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can't open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:16.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.71,0:11:18.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I used my usual strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.72,0:11:20.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:23.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't open the bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.39,0:11:24.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.74,0:11:25.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:26.60,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.56,0:11:30.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.52,0:11:35.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,How about we just tear it along the notches?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:35.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.67,0:11:36.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,O-One sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:37.63,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll open it so hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:42.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.97,0:11:44.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.14,0:11:46.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We can just tear along the notches or use scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.33,0:11:48.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that would hurt my pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:49.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or make me feel like a loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.26,0:12:01.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sister, is it a mosquito?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:02.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Mosquito!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.68,0:12:05.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you get annoyed when you know something's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:07.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when you haven't been bitten yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.31,0:12:08.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you know it's there...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.54,0:12:10.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you must take it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.29,0:12:12.98,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the instinct of a hunter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.35,0:12:16.56,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.27,0:12:21.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,If a guy in the same year professed his love for Yu-chan or me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.11,0:12:24.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...wouldn't that guy be a lolicon?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.28,0:12:27.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They're in the same class year...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:29.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so technically, they wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.33,0:12:33.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But in this case, it feels like appearance holds more weight...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.42,0:12:35.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, if...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.38,0:12:37.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...you were a 30-year-old who\N looked like someone in grade school...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.34,0:12:41.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you could say the guy likes older women...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:43.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a complicated issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.30,0:12:45.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to come up with a strict definition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.22,0:12:47.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're definitely my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.64,0:12:50.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami would have just ended it with, "Who cares?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:52.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So what about you, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.21,0:12:57.13,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(38,37)}Mom
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.29,0:12:55.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You fell in love with Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.92,0:12:57.13,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(350,35)}Daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:57.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and you dote on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.40,0:12:59.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...which means you're a lolicon, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.07,0:12:59.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.71,0:13:00.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.40,0:13:02.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not entirely accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.57,0:13:03.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not limited to little girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:05.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I also like normal girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:07.22,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So you should say that I'm {\i1}also{\i0} a lolicon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:09.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it basically depends on the character.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:12.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, you fail as a human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.50,0:13:13.25,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.25,0:13:16.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how you're always so clingy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:19.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you still be like that if I were a boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.07,0:13:22.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:22.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.99,0:13:24.19,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I totally understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.19,0:13:26.24,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you glad I'm a girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.34,0:13:28.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.39,0:13:30.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I think the bath should be ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.31,0:13:32.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You go first, Yu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.60,0:13:33.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.35,0:13:36.64,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He chased her away 'cause he was looking bad.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.31,0:13:39.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.27,0:13:41.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,About Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.98,0:13:43.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She was short...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.15,0:13:45.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...and your childhood friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.11,0:13:46.99,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she like a character out of a gal game?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:48.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.20,0:13:50.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She was adorable since she was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.68,0:13:53.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand why you fell for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.45,0:13:55.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but why did she marry you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.92,0:13:58.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was like, "You wouldn't accept me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:14:01.17,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I ended up as a gal game lover!"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.17,0:14:02.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And she just said yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:04.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're despicable!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:05.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:07.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that coercion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:08.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.55,0:14:10.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't the only reason, obviously...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:14.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And she was really happy when you were born...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.27,0:14:14.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:16.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't this mole make her look like you, Sou-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.35,0:14:18.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.14,0:14:20.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She has your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.15,0:14:22.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You can definitely tell she's our child.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.11,0:14:26.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But I hope she doesn't grow up like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:28.15,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope she doesn't inherit my height...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.15,0:14:30.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...or your personality...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:31.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty harsh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.53,0:14:35.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But why did you suddenly mention her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:39.00,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know much about Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.71,0:14:43.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.71,0:14:46.26,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you lonely without Mom around?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.30,0:14:48.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.43,0:14:51.39,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You create as much excitement as two people would.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.39,0:14:53.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And Yu-chan's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.85,0:14:55.43,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.43,0:14:56.31,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kanata...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.31,0:14:58.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Konata's grown up to be a good girl.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.89,0:15:01.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Though she's not as normal as you wanted...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.75,0:15:01.79,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(433,53)}A little geek
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:04.77,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.05,0:15:10.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't die before I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:13.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, I have no intention of doing so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.20,0:15:13.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.24,0:15:16.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata died young...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.70,0:15:19.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but she said she was happy and smiled at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.91,0:15:22.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard on those left behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.33,0:15:24.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I want to be like that at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.75,0:15:25.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Smiling?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.96,0:15:27.67,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So how do you want to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.34,0:15:28.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:30.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Death by over-arousal?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:33.47,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're definitely going to have a bizarre death!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.26,0:15:35.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.18,0:15:38.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought a digital camera for work today...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:15:58.97,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I haven't been back in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.50,0:16:00.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.83,0:16:01.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.41,0:16:02.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one more!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.19,0:16:03.02,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I wonder what...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:02.90,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:04.61,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez! I'm in the middle of a game!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:04.61,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}...they're doing right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.61,0:16:05.36,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:06.44,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:08.09,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.47,0:16:12.18,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, one more!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.51,0:16:13.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.72,0:16:15.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And Dad, you're way too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:17.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so heartless, Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.72,0:16:21.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We're taking photos to commemorate this new camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:22.85,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you buy this for work?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.27,0:16:25.08,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be such a stiff!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:24.63,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.63,0:16:26.63,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sou-kun hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.08,0:16:25.94,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,One more picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.94,0:16:26.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.63,0:16:28.50,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That's right, you never did...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:28.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a pest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.50,0:16:30.74,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}...pay much attention to what other people wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.74,0:16:31.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.88,0:16:32.32,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.32,0:16:33.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts, Konata!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.10,0:16:38.39,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You really haven't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:39.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.33,0:16:43.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You feel more and more like Kanata when I hold you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.37,0:16:44.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes my heart race.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.58,0:16:45.06,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.08,0:16:48.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't just blurt out risqué statements!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:51.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see what Mom had to put up with...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.55,0:16:52.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.78,0:16:54.15,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:55.61,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Your dad may be like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.61,0:16:57.49,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}...but don't turn into a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.18,0:16:59.35,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:17:02.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Teach me that one game once you clear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.89,0:17:04.10,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.10,0:17:06.52,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That one's surprisingly difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.75,0:17:07.63,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:10.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I made a wrong choice somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:09.55,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}They play games together...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.55,0:17:11.42,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}...so it looks like they're getting along.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.90,0:17:13.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't make it to the H-scene for the character I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.63,0:17:14.51,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:16.89,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What are you letting your daughter play?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:18.14,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:19.81,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Is this really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:22.31,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Aren't you teaching her the wrong things, Sou-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.41,0:17:24.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:27.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Mom choose you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.17,0:17:31.05,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause you're just a perverted, lolicon, old geek.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.05,0:17:32.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,People usually don't go for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.76,0:17:33.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a little harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:36.76,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't go easy on your old man, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:37.89,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}For real.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.89,0:17:39.41,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.74,0:17:39.99,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.43,0:17:41.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata had really good intuition.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:41.83,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You were always like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.93,0:17:45.46,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it was fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.33,0:17:45.48,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Always making me almost forget...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:48.75,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}...why I chose to spend...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.90,0:17:49.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I failed as a human being...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:52.59,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}...my life with this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.07,0:17:54.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...there was one thing I was absolutely sure about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.70,0:18:00.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,One thing you were absolutely sure about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.37,0:18:01.66,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.91,0:18:06.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.92,0:18:10.04,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...the one who loved Kanata most in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:16.45,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That was it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:20.16,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I just can't beat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:50.65,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(428,275)\frz30.841}Results for the New Writer Award
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:50.65,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(385,373)\frz30.841}No recipients
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:55.78,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}He accepts my good and bad parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:18:59.32,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}He's willing to show both...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:01.78,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}...his good and bad parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.50,0:19:09.87,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The place I feel most at ease...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.87,0:19:13.63,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The place that lets me feel most at ease...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.15,0:19:16.74,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:18.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:19.97,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough reminiscing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:21.20,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:23.72,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do one with Yu-chan later, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:25.26,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The fact that I can no longer be there...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.74,0:19:24.78,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.78,0:19:26.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And that would be more than one picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:26.91,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}...hurts a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.14,0:19:26.89,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.25,0:19:29.71,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You bought this for your hobby, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.71,0:19:30.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.62,0:19:31.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.88,0:19:35.30,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just testing it out before I take pictures for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:35.94,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.69,0:19:36.92,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:39.95,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}If I can live on inside them...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:43.45,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}...the way the two of them exist inside me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.70,0:19:46.66,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}...I'll continue to watch over them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.27,0:19:47.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:48.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:51.50,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}May the ones who brought me so much joy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.77,0:19:51.58,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:53.92,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}...be blessed with happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.58,0:19:54.11,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:19:59.92,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I wonder if they'll be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.45,0:20:01.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:02.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,This picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:07.12,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a shadow back there...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:08.79,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,A real ghost picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.43,0:20:10.18,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.41,0:20:12.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done with my bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.52,0:20:13.02,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:14.50,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Yu-Yu-Yu-Yu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:14.48,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:16.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,L-L-Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.59,0:20:17.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.21,0:20:17.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.55,0:20:19.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Delete it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.38,0:20:20.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to delete it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.80,0:20:21.88,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be cursed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:22.82,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}S-Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:23.86,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Don't delete it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.89,0:20:24.59,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.59,0:20:25.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Deleting it isn't enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:27.70,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't we have to burn it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:29.41,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Don't burn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.52,0:20:33.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I've talked with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.33,0:20:35.23,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...I have a different impression of her...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.23,0:20:38.55,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,...but Mina-rin still seems a little scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.55,0:20:40.82,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.32,0:20:42.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,She's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.64,0:20:45.34,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Minami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:46.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:47.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.49,0:20:50.10,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}Those two are really close.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.60,0:20:49.45,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You had classroom duty today, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.12,0:20:52.21,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Was the teacher still in the faculty office?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.48,0:20:52.18,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}This would be...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.54,0:20:54.83,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yutaka, your tie is crooked.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.83,0:20:56.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}B-Big Sister..{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.65,0:20:57.65,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I mustn't!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.65,0:20:59.53,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm looking at my friends weird again...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.53,0:21:01.49,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe it's been building up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:06.16,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.16,0:21:07.07,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:07.95,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.95,0:21:08.93,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.14,0:21:11.68,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,So did you find them?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.98,0:21:13.37,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't find them anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.37,0:21:14.48,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,And you can't find their managers?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.48,0:21:16.40,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,They ran away...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.40,0:21:18.29,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, either way, they're fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.77,0:21:18.31,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.31,0:21:19.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.11,0:21:20.23,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,It's rolling...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.13,0:21:22.38,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a bad feeling about this show from the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.24,0:21:23.42,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.38,0:21:23.13,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.13,0:21:23.80,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.82,0:21:25.86,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I actually refused in the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.86,0:21:27.57,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,But all that politics crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.57,0:21:29.14,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Grown-up issues and whatnot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.12,0:21:29.31,ls_alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.31,0:21:30.54,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, it's rolling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.95,0:21:31.91,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,What's rolling?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.91,0:21:32.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.27,0:21:32.73,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.73,0:21:33.75,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Or the earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.75,0:21:34.96,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.96,0:21:35.62,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.62,0:21:37.33,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying that the camera's rolling!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.33,0:21:37.81,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.81,0:21:38.27,ls_standard,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.75,0:21:41.53,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Isono!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.63,0:21:42.36,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Isono!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.38,0:21:43.17,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Nakajima?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.84,0:21:46.59,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, please listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.59,0:21:47.07,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,This time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.07,0:21:48.78,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, it's the medley version!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.91,0:22:58.52,ls_fo,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}1. Love Legend of Minoru 2. Forgot My Something 3. Sunny Sunshiny Happy 4. How a Man Should Live 5. Take it! Sailor Uniform 6. The Dentistman Song 7. My Dear Santa Monica
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.22,0:21:50.53,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three, four!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.53,0:21:51.99,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Mi-Mi-Miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.43,0:21:56.12,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,For-For-For-Forgot my something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.67,0:21:58.92,ls_ed_eng,,0000,0000,0000,,One clear, sunshiny day...
